Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Negros Occidental General Comprehensive High School in Bacolod City to Negros Occidental High School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 333
An Act Changing the Name of the Negros Occidental General Comprehensive High School in Bacolod City to Negros Occidental High School
Section 1. The name of the Negros Occidental General Comprehensive High School in Bacolod City is changed to Negros Occidental High School.1awp++i1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: January 19, 1983
